OL,5, A teenage girl's incurable cancer has  
OL,6, been cleared from her body in the first
OL,7, use of a revolutionary new type of     
OL,8, medicine.                              
OL,10,FAll other treatments for Alyssa's      
OL,11,Fleukaemia had failed.                  
OL,13,FSo doctors at Great Ormond Street      
OL,14,FHospital used "base editing" to perform
OL,15,Fa feat of biological engineering to    
OL,16,Fbuild her a new living drug.           
OL,18,FSix months later the cancer is         
OL,19,Fundetectable, but Alyssa is still being
OL,20,Fmonitored in case it comes back.       
